    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You make a magical proclamation, insisting that poisons will not harm your target as you touch them.</em></p><p><strong>Buff/Healing</strong> </p><ul><li><p>If the target is &amp;reference[Poisoned], you neutralize the poison, ending the condition and its secondary effects, if any. If more than one poison afflicts the target, you neutralize one poison that you know is present, or you neutralize one at random.</p></li><li><p>The target has advantage on saving throws against being &amp;reference[Poisoned] and has resistance to poison damage.</p></li></ul>",
            "chat": "<strong>Buff/Healing</strong> </p><ul><li><p>If the target is &amp;reference[Poisoned], you neutralize the poison, ending the condition and its secondary effects, if any. If more than one poison afflicts the target, you neutralize one poison that you know is present, or you neutralize one at random.</p></li><li><p>The target has advantage on saving throws against being &amp;reference[Poisoned] and has resistance to poison damage.</p></li></ul>"
